TH","ERE WERE NO INJURIES AS A RESULT OF THIS INCIDENT.  DAMAGE COSTS ASSOCIATED WITH THIS INCIDENT, INCL","UDING EQUIPMENT DAMAGE AND MAN POWER COSTS WERE- PS&C- $16,300.00; W&S $22,231.00.

SS&EM HAS DETE","RMINED THAT OPERATIONAL ERROR WAS THE PRIMARY CAUSAL FACTOR OF THIS DERAILMENT.
